1. *Obavi* svoju obavezu i dođi na sastanak. (Do your duty and come to the meeting.)
2. On je *obavio* posao brzo i efikasno. (He finished the job quickly and efficiently.)
3. *Obavljanje* kućnih poslova nije nimalo zabavno. (Doing household chores is not fun at all.)
4. Moramo *obaviti* još nekoliko telefonskih poziva prije nego što zatvorimo kancelariju. (We need to make a few more phone calls before we close the office.)
5. Molim te, *obavi* mi uslugu i donesi mi vodu. (Please do me a favor and bring me some water.)
6. Zadatak je bio težak, ali smo ga ipak *obavili* na vrijeme. (The task was difficult, but we managed to complete it on time.)
7. Oni obično *obavljaju* poslove u isto vrijeme svakog dana. (They usually perform their tasks at the same time every day.)
8. Uspjela sam *obaviti* sve što sam planirala danas. (I managed to do everything I planned today.)
9. *Obavljanje* posla bezvoljno često dovodi do loših rezultata. (Doing a job unwillingly often leads to poor results.)
10. *Obavljate* li usluge dostave hrane? (Do you provide food delivery services?)